{"tid":895458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛天警察要來了！杜拜警方投入飛行機車培訓","createTime":"2018-11-09T08:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T10:39:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f37f33c40e714a28f10e1061d745e1dbd952cc0f","tid":895458,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯無人機廠商Hoversurf去年與杜拜警方簽訂協議，提供了S3 2019 Hoverbike飛行機車設備，如今警察已投入訓練，預計在不遠的將來就可以在杜拜看到員警在天上飛。<br />\n <br />\n據《CNN》報導，杜拜警察局AI部門總監阿爾拉祖奇（Khalid Nasser Alrazooqi）表示，目前他們已投入2名人員進行訓練，並且還會增加訓練人數，目標是到2020年在警務行動中使用Hoverbike。<br />\n <br />\nHoversurf首席運營長Joseph Segura-Conn指出，理想的飛天機車駕駛，除了要有開摩托車的經驗之外，還要知道如何操作無人機。<br />\n <br />\n雖然杜拜警方擁有任意數量的採買權，不過一般民眾也是可以花15萬美元（約新台幣461萬元）購買，但Hoversurf仍然會對買家進行篩選，以確保他們能夠安全地駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/09/161913_b648d732c472f24178c11655e05ebc1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F161913_b648d732c472f24178c11655e05ebc1a.png&h=76066374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36cb05d4fdb52d1b97a181eab3033bbd6db03991","tid":895458,"uid":9470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"唔小心HI 到個幾塊葉 , 唔撚斷手都斷腳"},{"pid":"fe8bf3113d5c8e8720daa3b291cd262cf4c47de6","tid":895458,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"咁撚科幻既<br />\n好似拍D未來片先有咁"},{"pid":"c8676b520461f9236e6b075667f0829766a8290f","tid":895458,"uid":33643,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3204/d3204801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3204%2Fd3204801.jpg&h=83cc4598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9909e023974e6e1c844d6aef06e4034fa03cf1c","tid":895458,"uid":126100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36cb05d4fdb52d1b97a181eab3033bbd6db03991","tid":895458,"uid"